{"tid":1726873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府係要制造一個抗爭已完既假象","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:38.000Z","uid":54705,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab6e42cf1cd7f5544204556bb4bb6856ec9615a","tid":1726873,"uid":54705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"睇返今日咁多人&quot;自發&quot;清路障,連老解都出埋<br />\n清完D路就通返晒,又冇手足阻止,代表手足們都唔再抗爭,宣布抗爭已完<br />\n順便制造埋民意係企正苦果邊,呢招高招黎<br />\n<br />\n所以各位可以繼續開花,唔好俾佢停<br />\n星期六日就和你SHOP,其他日子快閃就得"},{"pid":"ded1be9fdedb75db1c6490f81a4b8d38eee2ce9d","tid":1726873,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"7809a5c09d77a5994bbf447efd7936aa635f2386","tid":1726873,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9cf525b4cff5c49d00b9b2d27e8449b0478ef0a","tid":1726873,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a759858b1f9f8159b06edd28df5d470513fa139","tid":1726873,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:34:02.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=dd09afad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=931d7a38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"45c65c88057acb573010052e6b7e67519ac6051f","tid":1726873,"uid":54705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e421c2b05a7b5836c4f6c7aa990befcdd9b1a9","tid":1726873